<p>In the project I have used a chart in the header of <code>UICollectionViewController</code> and when user taps on each <code>cell</code> the chart data is updated. Now I do not want the reuse header to be updated because of each time a <code>scrolling</code> chart ui is used.</p>  <p>in code</p>  <pre><code>collectionHeaderView = [self.collectionView dequeueReusableSupplementaryViewOfKind:UICollectionElementKindSectionHeader withReuseIdentifier:@"Header" forIndexPath:indexPath]; </code></pre>